        { n: '04', title: 'Add accessories gradually', text: 'Start with desk + chair + monitor. Add keyboard, webcam, and lighting over time as you identify what actually limits you.' },
        { n: '05', title: 'Watch Prime Day and Black Friday', text: 'Amazon typically offers 20‚Äì40% off electronics in July and November. Create a wishlist in advance and wait for the deals to hit.' },
      ].map(item => (
        <div class="flex gap-5 p-5 bg-oak-50 rounded-2xl border border-oak-100">
          <span class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-oak-300 shrink-0 leading-none">{item.n}</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-ink mb-1">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">{item.text}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section id="faq" class="scroll-mt-24 mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      {[
        {
          q: 'What\'s the minimum budget for a decent home office setup?',
          a: 'Budget at minimum $300‚Äì400: a basic desk ($50‚Äì80), an entry-level ergonomic chair ($100‚Äì150), and a 24" monitor ($130‚Äì170). Below this, you\'ll make compromises on comfort that impact long-term productivity and health.',
        },
        {
          q: 'Should I buy everything at once or gradually?',
          a: 'Gradually, in this order: chair ‚Üí monitor ‚Üí desk ‚Üí accessories. The chair is the absolute priority ‚Äî it directly impacts your posture and long-term back health. Once those three are in place, add peripherals as you identify your specific pain points.',
        },
        {
          q: 'Are refurbished products reliable for a home office?',
          a: 'Yes, especially through Amazon Renewed (90-day guarantee) or certified refurbished programs. For monitors, refurbished is excellent value. For chairs, look for remanufactured options from known brands ‚Äî reprofessionally restored to original specs with new foam and fabric.',
        },
      ].map(item => (
